{"title":"我望着你","date":"2018-04-18T15:49:44.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年4月18日","L":"2018/04/18","MM-DD":"04-18"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/30/O9pMqfTikP5QLXy.jpg","link":"2018/04/18/我望着你","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-02-10T16:58:58.917Z","content":"<p>我痴然地望着你<br>阳光下温暖的草地<br>松软的土壤<br>泥土里混着迷乱的气息  </p>\n<p>我望着你<br>你还是你  </p>\n<p>我用力地拥抱着你<br>沐浴和煦的朝曦<br>伸进疏酥的泥土<br>放肆这自然的气息  </p>\n<p>我抱着你<br>你的怀里不是你</p>\n","prev":{"title":"到站了","link":"2018/04/30/到站了"},"next":{"title":"只为再见到你","link":"2018/04/16/只为再见到你"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/18/我望着你/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦树下的人","link":"<a href=\"http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/18/我望着你/\" title=\"我望着你\">http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/18/我望着你/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}